sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant HTTP as HTTP Layer
    participant Engine as ExecutionGraphQlService
    participant Controller as @Controller
    participant MixSvc as MixSessionService
    participant VoteSvc as CrowdVoteService
    participant MixPort as MixSessionUpdatePort
    participant VotePort as CrowdVoteTallyPort
    participant MixPub as MixSessionUpdatePublisher
    participant VotePub as CrowdVoteTallyPublisher

    note over Client,HTTP: Query / Mutation — HTTP POST /graphql
    Client->>HTTP: POST /graphql
    HTTP->>Engine: execute(RequestInput)
    Engine->>Controller: @QueryMapping / @MutationMapping
    Controller->>MixSvc: session mutations (crowdCheered, …)
    MixSvc-->>Controller: MixSession
    Controller->>VoteSvc: vote mutations (castCrowdVote, …)
    VoteSvc-->>Controller: VoteTally
    Controller-->>Engine: resolved value
    note over Engine,Controller: @SchemaMapping resolvers called<br/>for each requested nested field
    Engine-->>Client: JSON { data: ... }

    note over Client,VotePub: Mutation side-effects → Subscriptions (output ports)
    MixSvc--)MixPort: publish(MixSession)
    MixPort--)MixPub: tryEmitNext(session)
    MixPub--)Client: mixSessionUpdated via WebSocket
    VoteSvc--)VotePort: publish(VoteTally)
    VotePort--)VotePub: tryEmitNext(tally)
    VotePub--)Client: crowdVoteTallyUpdated via WebSocket
